</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>SpaceX 火箭發射塔公開 Elon Musk 親自拍片做導遊</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/04/spacex-musk/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=spacex-musk</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 04 Jun 2022 04:43:13 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[SpaceX]]></category><category><![CDATA[Stage Zero]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1101993</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>YouTube 頻道 Everyday Astronaut 近日上傳一條 Elon Musk 登上用作發射 S [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">YouTube 頻道 Everyday Astronaut 近日上傳一條 Elon Musk 登上用作發射 SpaceX 火箭的發射塔。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">發射塔位於美國布朗斯維爾附近的 SpaceX 星港，建有名為 Stage Zero 的巨型機械臂，用作固定即將發射及剛著陸的火箭。Musk 曾於 Twitter 上指，Stage Zero 如火箭推進器及太空船般，是火箭發射及著陸必備的裝置，而影片中的 Musk 則不禁興奮地讚嘆著 Stage Zero。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">由 Stage Zero 固定的銀色火箭推進器直徑約 9 米，重約 250 噸，可透過頂部的紅色金屬配件被懸掛半空。當火箭著陸時，火箭會減速衝向 Stage Zero 兩臂間，Stage Zero 便會緊鉤火箭的第一助推器，再收臂接住火箭。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.04-1.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102016" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.04-1-694x311.png" alt="" width="694" height="311" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.04-1-694x311.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.04-1-1280x574.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.04-1-768x344.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.04-1-1536x689.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.04-1-2048x919.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.04-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：影片截圖<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.22.png"><br /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">影片內的 Elon Musk 更與記者乘搭 Stage Zero 內的電梯到達頂層。由於 Stage Zero 高 143 米，因此 Elon Musk 與記者站在離地面約 138 米的頂層，兩人對 Stage Zero 外的景色感到驚訝，Musk 更笑稱計劃在 Stage Zero 頂層加設高空滑索設施。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.22.png"><br /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.22-1.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102013" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.22-1-694x317.png" alt="" width="694" height="317" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.22-1-694x317.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.22-1-1280x585.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.22-1-768x351.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.22-1-1536x702.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.22-1-2048x936.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.22-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.31-1.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102014" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.31-1-694x317.png" alt="" width="694" height="317" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.31-1-694x317.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.31-1-1280x584.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.31-1-768x351.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.31-1-1536x701.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.31-1-2048x935.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.28.31-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>圖片來源：影片截圖</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Elon Musk 表示，可重複使用的 SpaceX 火箭就如飛機般，能成為人類提供往返不同星球的工具。由於研發可重用火箭除了需應付地球重力及大氣密度外，亦需適用於不同星球的境外，令研發可重用火箭的難度大大提升。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.45-1.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102015" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.45-1-694x341.png" alt="" width="694" height="341" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.45-1-694x341.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.45-1-1280x628.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.45-1-768x377.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.45-1-1536x754.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.45-1-2048x1005.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-27-13.29.45-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>圖片來源：影片截圖</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_64775"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XP5k3ZzPf_0?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfu