</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Google AI 輸入文字後可生成圖像，騎呢古怪文字都可變圖片</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/04/imagen/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=imagen</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 04 Jun 2022 04:41:44 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[google]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google Brain]]></category><category><![CDATA[Imagen]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1102268</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Google 推出全新文本生成圖像 AI 工具「Imagen」，並公開一系列由 Imagen 生成的圖片。 &#038; [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Google 推出全新文本生成圖像 AI 工具「Imagen」，並公開一系列由 Imagen 生成的圖片。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Google 旗下深度學習與人工智慧科研專案團隊 Google Brain，近日發布了一系列由新的文本生成圖像 AI 工具「Imagen」製出的成果。Imagen 透過解析用家所輸入的文字而生成寫實的圖像，更能突破人類的想像力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-1-e1653470412447.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102284" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-1-e1653470412447-580x580.png" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-1-e1653470412447-580x580.png 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-1-e1653470412447-120x120.png 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-1-e1653470412447.png 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">在雪地裡戴著空手道腰帶的火龍果。（A dragon fruit wearing karate belt in the snow.）</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-3-e1653470435622.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102286" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-3-e1653470435622-580x580.png" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-3-e1653470435622-580x580.png 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-3-e1653470435622-120x120.png 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-3-e1653470435622.png 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">機械人在水浸的莫奈美術展覽中使用槳板。</p><p style="text-align: center;">（An art gallery displaying Monet paintings. The art gallery is flooded. Robots are going around the art gallery using paddle boards.）</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-5-e1653470451832.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102287" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-5-e1653470451832-580x580.png" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-5-e1653470451832-580x580.png 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-5-e1653470451832-120x120.png 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-5-e1653470451832.png 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">泰迪熊在奧運 400 米蝶泳項目中游泳。（Teddy bears swimming at the Olympics 400m Butterfly event.）</p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源： Google</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Google 透過 DrawBench 圖像模型基準測試來評估 Imagen 的文字生成圖像能力，較 VQ-GAN、LDM 及 DALL-E 2 等同類型工具比，Imagen 生成的圖像逼真度更高，語言理解能力亦更好，與輸入的文字較為符合，偏好率更高達 50%。與 DALL-E 2 相比，Imagen 能準確地為圖像配色，而 DALL-E 2 則容易混淆多個顏色指令的文字。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-8.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-8-587x580.png" alt="" width="587" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-8-587x580.png 587w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-8-120x120.png 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/google-brain-imagen-8.png 698w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 587px" /></a>圖片來源： Google</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Google 表示，由於 Imagen 在生成圖像過程的評估工作尚有不足，導致在生成圖像時出現一些社會和文化偏見，亦傾向西方對性別的刻板印象，例如膚色及對職業的描繪，更出現色情圖像、種族主義攻擊言論等的不當內容。因此在有關問題修復前，將不會對外開放 Imagen 的程式碼，更不會對外展示。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.deccanherald.com/business/technology/google-imagen-new-ai-tool-can-conjure-up-realistic-photos-from-just-text-description-1112950.html">Deccan Herald</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">—</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
